TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Sq query fetches from claim snapshot table data which comes between snapshot start and end date range to truncate the partition.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_WC_FIN_CLAIMS_SNAPSHOT_POST_LOAD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: Select row_wid,calendar_date,Decode(row_wid,m_end_cal_dt_wid,'Y','N') month_end_flg from W_DAY_D wd where (('D' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' /* 'D' or 'M' or 'R' */ and wd.calendar_date BETWEEN trunc(to_date('$$SNAPSHOT_START_DT','MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) AND (trunc(sysdate) - 1) and wd.calendar_date >= trunc(sysdate, 'MM') ) or ('M' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' /* 'D' or 'M' or 'R' */ and wd.calendar_date = trunc(sysdate, 'MM') - 1) or ('R' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' /* 'D' or 'M' or 'R' */ and wd.calendar_date between TO_DATE('$$RECON_STRT_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') /* Reconcile start date */ and TO_DATE('$$RECON_END_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') /* Reconcile end date */ and (wd.calendar_date >= trunc(sysdate, 'MM') or wd.calendar_date = last_day(wd.calendar_date))))

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This expression, call the truncate partition stored procedure for the records which will be reconcilled.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_TRUNCATE_PARTITION

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF($$SNPSHOT_FLG='D', IIF( NOT ISNULL(:LKP.WC_LKP_WC_FIN_CLAIMS_SNAPSHOT(SNAPSHOT_DT_WID)), ERROR('User defined error: An attempt was made to truncate an existing snapshot without setting the $$SNPSHOT_FLG=R OR M. Either set this flag = R and provide reconcile start date and end date Or set this flag = M in case previous month snapshot is required.') ), :SP.SP_WC_TRUNCATETABLE_PARTITION(v_OWNER_NAME,v_TABLE_NAME,v_PARTITION_NAME,v_CUT_OF_START_DT,v_CUT_OF_END_DT,v_STATUS))
--- If Snapshot flag is 'D' i.e. Daily load -- If Snapshot exists in table raises Application error --- Else truncate partition for given date range
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: v_CALL_TRUNC_PARTITION

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Lookup is added to filter out $0 transaction from claims. Look up will look only non Invoice related claims. Developer - Nitin Garg Project - 49269 ( July -2018 Release)
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT SNAPSHOT_DT_WID AS SNAPSHOT_DT_WID, RECEIPT_NUMBER AS RECEIPT_NUMBER, DATASOURCE_NUM_ID AS DATASOURCE_NUM_ID, REMAINING_DOC_AMT AS REMAINING_DOC_AMT FROM (SELECT W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID SNAPSHOT_DT_WID, RECEIPT_NUMBER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.DATASOURCE_NUM_ID, SUM(REMAINING_DOC_AMT) REMAINING_DOC_AMT FROM WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F, W_DAY_D DUEDT, W_DAY_D INVOICEDT, (select calendar_date, ROW_WID from W_DAY_D wd where (('D' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' and wd.calendar_date BETWEEN trunc(to_date('$$SNAPSHOT_START_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) AND (trunc(sysdate) - 1) and wd.calendar_date >= trunc(sysdate, 'MM')) or ('M' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' and wd.calendar_date = trunc(sysdate, 'MM') - 1) or ('R' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' and wd.calendar_date between TO_DATE('$$RECON_STRT_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and TO_DATE('$$RECON_END_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and (wd.calendar_date >= trunc(sysdate, 'MM') or wd.calendar_date = last_day(wd.calendar_date))))) W_DAY_D_Dim WHERE INV_RLTD_CLAIM_FLG = 'N' AND WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID = DUEDT.ROW_WID AND WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID = INVOICEDT.ROW_WID AND ((((WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID <= w_day_d_dim.row_wid and WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID <> 0 ) or ((WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID > w_day_d_dim.row_wid and WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID <> 0 )))
and (WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID = 0 or WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID > w_day_d_dim.row_wid)) or (WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID <> 0 and WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID <= w_day_d_dim.row_wid and substr(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID, 0, 6) = substr(w_day_d_dim.row_wid, 0, 6) and WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.STATUS = 'CLOSED')) GROUP BY W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID, RECEIPT_NUMBER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.DATASOURCE_NUM_ID HAVING SUM(REMAINING_DOC_AMT) <> 0)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SNAPSHOT_DT_WID = in_SNAPSHOT_DT_WID AND RECEIPT_NUMBER = in_RECEIPT_NUMBER AND DATASOURCE_NUM_ID = in_DATASOURCE_NUM_ID

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
SELECT W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID, W_DAY_D_Dim.CALENDAR_DATE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CUSTOMER_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CUSTOMER_ACCT_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CUSTOMER_FIN_PROFL_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CUSTOMER_BILL_TO_LOC_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_NUMBER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_TYPE_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_TYPE_DESC, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.INV_RLTD_CLAIM_FLG, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_OWNER_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CREATED_BY_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.LAST_UPDATED_BY_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CREATION_DATE_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_STRT_DATE_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_ACTL_END_DATE_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIMS_LAST_UPDATE_DATE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CUST_TRX_LAST_UPDATE_DATE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIMS_TL_LAST_UPDATE_DATE, SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ORIG_CLAIM_DOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ORIG_CLAIM_LOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ADJUSTED_DOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ADJUSTED_LOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.REMAINING_DOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.REMAINING_LOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.SETTLED_DOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.SETTLED_LOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ACCTD_DOC_AMT), SUM(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ACCTD_LOC_AMT), WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.DOC_CURRENCY_CODE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.LOC_CURRENCY_CODE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_REASON_CODE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_REASON_DESC, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.STATUS, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRANSACTION_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRANSACTION_TYPE, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.SALES_INVOICE_NUM, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.RECEIPT_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.RECEIPT_NUMBER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.PAYMENT_METHOD, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.DEDUCTION_REP_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.APPLIED_RECEIPT_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.APPLIED_RECEIPT_NUMBER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.APPROVED_BY_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.SETTLED_BY_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.ETN_LEDGER, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CREDIT_OFFICE, CASE WHEN (MAX(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID) > W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID) THEN 'N' ELSE 'Y' END AS OVER_DUE_FLAG, CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 30 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 0 THEN 1 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 60 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 31 THEN 2 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 90 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 61 THEN 3 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 180 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 91 THEN 4 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 360 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 181 THEN 5 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 720 AND ABS(MAX(DUEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 361 THEN 6 ELSE 7 END) END) END) END) END) END AS AGING_BUCKET, CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 30 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 0 THEN 1 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 60 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 31 THEN 2 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 90 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 61 THEN 3 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 180 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 91 THEN 4 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 360 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 181 THEN 5 ELSE (CASE WHEN ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) <= 720 AND ABS(MAX(INVOICEDT.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) - W_DAY_D_Dim.JULIAN_DAY_NUM) >= 361 THEN 6 ELSE 7 END) END) END) END) END) END AS OPEN_BUCKET, CASE WHEN MAX(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID) > W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID AND MAX(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID) < W_DAY_D_Dim.m_end_cal_dt_wid THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END current_mnth_due_flg, CASE WHEN MAX(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID) > W_DAY_D_Dim.ROW_WID AND MAX(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.TRX_DATE_WID) > W_DAY_D_Dim.m_end_cal_dt_wid THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END future_due_flg, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.DATASOURCE_NUM_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.INTEGRATION_ID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.OPERATING_UNIT_ORG_WID, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.X_REASON_NAME, WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.CLAIM_DATE_WID, --Added Claim Date under Defect 17137 identified during INT 3 CLAIM_SLA.GL_ACCOUNT_WID, -- Added as part of INC000011029842 WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.x_Unify_Cust_Bill_To_Ref_Wid, --Project - 49269 ( July 2018) NVL(WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.X_CLOSED_DATE_WID,0), -- Added as part of project 50390 for INC000011462060 WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F.X_CUST_REF_NUM -- Added as part of project 50390 for INC000011640315 FROM WC_FIN_CLAIMS_F, W_DAY_D DUEDT, W_DAY_D INVOICEDT, (select * from W_DAY_D wd where (('D' = '$$SNPSHOT_FLG' /* 'D' or 'M' or 'R' */ and wd.calendar_date BETWEEN trunc(to_date('$$SNAPSHOT_START_DT', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')) AND (trunc(sysdate) -
